<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM14.3">
<l>mālāyp piṟanta nampiyai mālē ceyyu maṇāḷaṉai</l>
<l>ēlāp poyka ḷuraippāṉai yiṅkē pōtak kaṇṭīrē</l>
<l>mēlāṟ paranta veyilkāppāṉ viṉatai ciṟuvaṉ ciṟakeṉṉu</l>
<l>mēlāp piṉkīḻ varuvāṉai viruntā vaṉattē kaṇṭōmē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Did you see the Lord—who is love incarnate, the Bridegroom who causes confusion,</l>
<l>He who speaks unacceptable lies—go this [way]?</l>
<l>We saw Him in Bṛndāvana He who comes under the canopy</l>
<l>That is the wing of Vinatā’s boy (Garuḍa) in order to guard against</l>
<l rend="indent">The heat spread above.</l> 
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
